<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>CCE — Engineer Control Center</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --teal-dark:   #003d33;
      --teal:        #00695c;
      --teal-mid:    #00897b;
      --teal-light:  #26a69a;
      --teal-pale:   #b2dfdb;
      --accent:      #00e5cc;
      --bg:          #f0f4f3;
      --card:        #ffffff;
      --text:        #1a2624;
      --muted:       #607d79;
      --radius:      14px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ─── NAVBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 40px;
      height: 64px;
      background: rgba(0, 61, 51, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--teal-pale); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: .5px;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--accent); color: var(--teal-dark) !important;
      padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700 !important;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: #00fff2 !important; color: var(--teal-dark) !important; }

    /* hamburger */
    .hamburger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
    .hamburger span { width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--teal-pale); border-radius: 2px; transition: .3s; }

    /* ─── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-dark) 0%, #006655 50%, var(--teal) 100%);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px 60px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(0,229,204,.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 30%, rgba(0,137,123,.25) 0%, transparent 55%);
    }
    .hero-grid {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,204,.07) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,229,204,.07) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
    }
    .hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 780px; }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(0,229,204,.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,204,.4);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 6px 18px; border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
      font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -2px;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hero-content h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem);
      color: var(--teal-pale);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent); color: var(--teal-dark);
      padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,229,204,.4);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,229,204,.55); }
    .btn-outline {
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(0,229,204,.1); }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 64px;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num {
      font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
      display: block; line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--teal-pale); letter-spacing: .5px; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ─── SECTION WRAPPER ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .section { padding: 100px 20px; }
    .section-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(0,137,123,.12);
      color: var(--teal-mid);
      font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
      font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-title span { color: var(--teal-mid); }
    .section-desc {
      font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7; max-width: 580px;
    }

    /* ─── ABOUT / FEATURES ───────────────────────────────────── */
    #features { background: #fff; }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px; margin-top: 60px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid #e0ebe9;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 30px 26px;
      transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,105,92,.12); }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-mid), var(--teal-light));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,137,123,.3);
    }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .feature-card p { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ─── HOW IT WORKS ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    #how {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, #e8f5f3 100%);
    }
    .steps {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;
      margin-top: 60px; position: relative;
    }
    .steps::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; left: 35px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--teal-mid), var(--teal-pale));
    }
    .step {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 28px;
      padding: 30px 0; position: relative;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-dark), var(--teal-mid));
      color: #fff; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 900;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,105,92,.35);
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .step-body h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .step-body p  { font-size: .95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; max-width: 580px; }

    /* ─── METRICS / HUD PREVIEW ──────────────────────────────── */
    #hud { background: var(--teal-dark); color: #fff; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    #hud::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(0,229,204,.12) 0%, transparent 65%);
    }
    .hud-wrap {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px;
      align-items: center; position: relative;
    }
    .hud-text .section-tag { background: rgba(0,229,204,.15); color: var(--accent); }
    .hud-text .section-title { color: #fff; }
    .hud-text .section-desc { color: var(--teal-pale); max-width: 460px; }
    .hud-metrics {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;
    }
    .metric-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,204,.2);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 22px 18px;
      transition: background .3s;
    }
    .metric-card:hover { background: rgba(0,229,204,.1); }
    .metric-label { font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: 1.2px; color: var(--teal-pale); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .metric-value {
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
      margin: 6px 0 2px; line-height: 1;
    }
    .metric-unit { font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }
    .metric-bar-wrap { margin-top: 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); border-radius: 4px; height: 5px; }
    .metric-bar { height: 5px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--accent); }

    /* ─── SCREENSHOTS ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #screenshots { background: #fff; }
    .screens-row {
      display: flex; gap: 24px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }
    .screen-mock {
      width: 200px; background: var(--teal-dark);
      border-radius: 26px; overflow: hidden;
      border: 4px solid var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,77,64,.25);
      transition: transform .3s;
    }
    .screen-mock:hover { transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.03); }
    .screen-top {
      background: var(--teal); height: 36px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .screen-top-dot {
      width: 60px; height: 8px; background: var(--teal-dark);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .screen-body { padding: 14px 12px; }
    .screen-title {
      font-size: .6rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .screen-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .screen-label { font-size: .55rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }
    .screen-val { font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
    .screen-mini-bar { height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .screen-mini-bar-fill { height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; }
    .screen-circle {
      width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      margin: 10px auto;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
    }
    .screen-caption {
      text-align: center; font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 14px; font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ─── DOWNLOAD ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #download {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-dark) 0%, #00574b 100%);
      text-align: center;
    }
    #download .section-title { color: #fff; }
    #download .section-desc { color: var(--teal-pale); margin: 0 auto 40px; }
    .download-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .store-btn {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      color: #fff; text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 26px; border-radius: 14px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      transition: background .25s, border-color .25s, transform .25s;
    }
    .store-btn:hover {
      background: rgba(0,229,204,.15);
      border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .store-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
    .store-text-top { font-size: .65rem; color: var(--teal-pale); display: block; }
    .store-text-bot { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; display: block; }
    .qr-note { margin-top: 36px; font-size: .85rem; color: var(--teal-pale); }

    /* ─── CONTACT ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #contact { background: var(--bg); }
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 50px;
      margin-top: 60px; align-items: start;
    }
    .contact-info h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .contact-info p { font-size: .95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }
    .contact-info a { color: var(--teal-mid); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .contact-info a:hover { color: var(--teal-dark); }
    .contact-items { margin-top: 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .contact-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #dde8e6;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 18px;
    }
    .contact-item-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-mid), var(--teal-light));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .contact-item-text { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
    .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
    .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .form-group label { font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: .5px; }
    .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px 14px;
      border: 1.5px solid #dde8e6;
      border-radius: 10px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: .92rem; background: #fff; color: var(--text);
      outline: none; transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus {
      border-color: var(--teal-mid);
    }
    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 110px; }
    .btn-submit {
      background: var(--teal-mid); color: #fff;
      border: none; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    footer {
      background: var(--teal-dark); color: var(--teal-pale);
      padding: 50px 20px 28px;
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .footer-brand-name {
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .footer-brand-desc {
      font-size: .87rem; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      max-width: 260px;
    }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .footer-col a {
      font-size: .87rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .2s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 24px auto 0;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;
    }

    /* ─── SCROLL ANIMATIONS ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity .55s ease, transform .55s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hud-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      nav { padding: 0 20px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; flex-direction: column; position: fixed; top: 64px; left: 0; right: 0; background: var(--teal-dark); padding: 24px; gap: 20px; }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }
      .hud-metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .steps::before { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAVBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#hero">CCE</a>
  <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
    <li><a href="#how">How It Works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#hud">HUD</a></li>
    <li><a href="#screenshots">Preview</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    <li><a href="/app" class="nav-cta">⚡ Launch App</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="hamburger" id="hamburger" onclick="toggleNav()">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">⚡ Engineering Control Center</div>
    <h1><span>CCE</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      The professional HUD app for engineers and facility managers to monitor,
      control, and optimize energy & water consumption in real time.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="/app" class="btn-primary">⚡ Launch App</a>
      <a href="#features" class="btn-outline">Explore Features</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">99%</span><span class="stat-label">Uptime</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">Real-Time</span><span class="stat-label">Data Updates</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">30%</span><span class="stat-label">Avg Cost Reduction</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">∞</span><span class="stat-label">Sensor Support</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── FEATURES ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="features" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-tag">Core Features</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything an engineer <span>needs</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">CCE packs professional-grade monitoring tools into a sleek, fast, mobile interface built for the field.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Real-Time Energy Monitoring</h3>
        <p>Track kWh, voltage, current, and power factor live. Drill into circuits and phases with sub-second refresh.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">💧</div>
        <h3>Water Consumption Control</h3>
        <p>Monitor flow rates, pressure, and total usage across multiple zones. Detect leaks before they become costly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">🖥️</div>
        <h3>Interactive HUD Interface</h3>
        <p>A clean, heads-up display puts every critical metric front and center — designed for speed in busy environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Analytics & Forecasting</h3>
        <p>Visualize trends, compare periods, and use built-in forecasting to plan capacity and budget ahead of time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
        <h3>Smart Alerts</h3>
        <p>Set custom thresholds for any metric. Get push notifications the moment something goes out of range.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔌</div>
        <h3>Sensor & API Integration</h3>
        <p>Connect directly to industrial sensors, SCADA systems, or manual data input. Works with any facility setup.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
        <h3>Android & iOS</h3>
        <p>Native apps for both platforms — optimized for tablets and phones. Works offline with sync when reconnected.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Secure & Role-Based Access</h3>
        <p>Assign permissions per team member. All data encrypted in transit and at rest — enterprise-ready security.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="how" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-tag">How It Works</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Up and running in <span>minutes</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">No complex setup. CCE is designed to connect to your facility and deliver insights fast.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
